                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with a previous conviction of embezzlement at Middlesex Sessions in</hi> 1868, <hi rend="italic">when he was sentenced to Two Years Imprison-ment, to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.**—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18730303-240-punishment-20" type="punishmentDescription">
